a-aid=\"128346136\" id=\"note9a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"tg\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel?lang=eng\"><small>TG</small> Apostasy of Israel</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note9b\" data-full-marker=\"9b\">\n<p data-aid=\"128346137\" id=\"note9b_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/gen/18.20-21?lang=eng#p20\">Gen. 18:20 (20–21)</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/gen/19.24-25?lang=eng#p5\">19:5, 24 (24–25)</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.19?lang=eng#p19\">2 Ne. 23:19</a>. </span><span data-note-category=\"tg\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/homosexual-behavior?lang=eng\"><small>TG</small> Homosexual Behavior</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"10\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note10a\" data-full-marker=\"10a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128346138\" id=\"note10a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/deut/12.28?lang=eng#p28\">Deut. 12:28</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note10b\" data-full-marker=\"10b\">\n<p data-aid=\"128346139\" id=\"note10b_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ps/128.2?lang=eng#p2\">Ps. 128:2</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"12\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note12a\" data-full-marker=\"12a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128346140\" id=\"note12a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/9.16?lang=eng#p16\">Isa. 9:16</a>. </span><span data-note-category=\"tg\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/leadership?lang=eng\"><small>TG</small> Leadership</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"13\">\n<ul c